name: Cycling Socks
description:
The "Peace, Love and Pedals" cycling sock will likely be the most comfortable and fun you've ever worn! The socks are manufactured by Sockguy and is 'one size fits most' (approximately sizes 6 to 11).

Free shipping to the 48 contiguous United States!

name: The Bronx Cycling Jersey - A TOP SELLING cycling jersey for men and women!
description:
It feels good to represent! :)

Love the New York City borough of the Bronx? You'll feel great and proud wearing a cycling jersey that represents the Bronx while enjoying a ride on your bike. This jersey is stylish, comfortable and makes a statement!

Represent The Bronx with this stylish cycling jersey! A slanted “The” preceding “Bronx” and splashes of purple make this a stylish and unique jersey and an all-time favorite by many who pedal a bike. Printed on the sleeves and collar is “The Boogie Down”, reminiscent of the Bronx’s role as an incubator of Hip-Hop.

name: Brooklyn Cycling Jersey - A TOP SELLING cycling jersey for men and women!
description:
It feels good to represent! :)

Love the New York City borough of Brooklyn? You'll feel great and proud wearing a cycling jersey that represents Brooklyn while enjoying a ride on your bike. This jersey is stylish, comfortable and makes a statement!

Represent the NYC borough of Brooklyn in style while navigating the Brooklyn Bridge with its maze of joggers, tourists and the generally disoriented! The Brooklyn jersey is bright, fresh and hip, just like the Brooklyn we know today. A dash of nostalgia is inscribed on the sleeves and collar with the phrase; “No sleep til…”.

name: 'Da Bronx' Cycling Cap - Back in Stock!!!
description:
This "Peace, Love and Pedals" Bronx cycling cap is stylish, hip and comfy! It features the popular "Peace, Love & Pedals" logo on the back, "Bx" on the front of the crown, a cool "Boogie Down Bronx" icon on each side and "Da Bronx" on the top and bottom of the bill. Fits most sized heads comfortably. 

Now available in 3, 5 and 10 packs! Each pack gets you a better deal. Your friends will not only thank you but also think you're a hero for giving them a Bronx cycling cap. The multi-packs are perfect for gift-giving and achieving super-hero status amongst your friends and family. :)

Free shipping to the 48 contiguous United States!

name: San Francisco Cycling Jersey - Sales of this jersey benefits Trips for Kids!

It feels good to represent! :) 

Love San Francisco? You'll feel great and proud wearing a cycling jersey that represents San Francisco while enjoying a ride on your bike. This jersey is stylish, comfortable and makes a statement!

Represent San Francisco in style while riding anywhere around the world! This cycling jersey is bright, fresh and hip, just like the city itself. Printed on the collar and sleeves is "The city by the bay".

name: Singlespeeder Cycling Jersey - An Urban and Offroad Cycling Jersey Classic for men and women!
description:

Love your singlespeed bike? You'll feel great and proud wearing a cycling jersey that represents singlespeeding while enjoying a ride on your bike. This jersey is stylish, comfortable and makes a statement!

name: Queens Cycling Jersey - A Peace, Love & Pedals cycling jersey classic for men and women!
description:
It feels good to represent! :)

Love the New York City borough of Queens? You'll feel great and proud wearing a cycling jersey that represents Queens while enjoying a ride on your bike. This jersey is stylish, comfortable and makes a statement!

Which NYC borough is the most ethnically diverse? Yup, Queens! With close to half the population foreign-born, representing over 100 different countries and speaking 130+ different languages, Queens is tops in diversity. The Queens cycling jersey celebrates this diversity with the phrase “Melting Pot” printed on the sleeves and collar.

description:

The borough of Staten Island is, at times, known as the “forgotten borough”. Remind the good citizens of the other four boroughs that Staten Island is, in fact, alive and kicking while wearing the Staten Island jersey! On the sleeves and collar is the phrase: “Don’t forget SI!”

name: Manhattan Cycling Jersey - A Peace, Love & Pedals cycling jersey classic for men and women!
description:
It feels good to represent! :)

Love the New York City borough of Manhattan? You'll feel great and proud wearing a cycling jersey that represents Manhattan while enjoying a ride on your bike. This jersey is stylish, comfortable and makes a statement!

Black is always ‘in’ in Manhattan while apples, yes apples, are red. With red and black as the dominant colors of the Manhattan jersey, you’ll be pedaling the city streets in style!
